<br>
IF a raid is fighting on the entrance ledge to HoT, and you have NO KOS people there, will the mobs from the hub assist an HOT mob if someone opens the door?<br>
<br>
This is not a flame, nor is it going to turn into one by me. I just want a REAL answer from people that have been there and know. As far as I am aware, they will assist. I have seen to door opened and people were aggro'd and killed, however they were from another guild so I am not aware of their faction. I've gotten mixed messages about this, so I'm just looking to clear it up.<br>
<br>
Thank you for any legit answers. Flamers or wanna be flamers, please see recent threads in R&amp;F and leave this one alone.<br>
 <p><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=205403"><IMG SRC="http://lucidchimera.freeservers.com/images/Dexlen.jpg" WIDTH=105 HEIGHT=200 ALIGN=LEFT></A><BR><BR><BR><BR><BR><BR><BR><BR><BR><BR>
