om/ucorpsedagain.showPublicProfile?language=EN>CorpsedAgain</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Senior Member</span><br>  Posts: 928<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(10/12/02 2:37:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3358.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: HoT Door (just a question, not a flame)</span><hr size=1> Why dont we put this question with haste cap, and things like that.  Bottom line is some people are sure that it DOES cause aggro, and some are sure that it DOES NOT.  Solution:  Ask before you open the door to be safe and to respect any guild fighting on other side. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=198911>Corpsed</a>
